I've got a number of them
scattered around my home.

00:00:15.550 --> 00:00:17.970
And some of you may as well.

00:00:17.970 --> 00:00:20.510
But it's great to have
Rodney here.

00:00:20.510 --> 00:00:21.982
Thanks for coming.

