I did that on purpose--

00:00:56.850 --> 00:00:59.990
and Chris James from the
legal department.

00:00:59.990 --> 00:01:03.560
Well, I better start my little
starter, my little clock.

00:01:03.560 --> 00:01:06.950
And a lady by the name of Lisa
Brewer, who is one of my

00:01:06.950 --> 00:01:10.660
people at the gallery I
have in San Francisco.

00:01:10.660 --> 00:01:12.900
It's a 14,000 square-foot
gallery.

